channel.title: What game is this?
channel.description:
I've been searching for a while for a game I can't remember the title of. The main problem is that there's only one part that I remember, but it sounds interesting enough to play the game again.
All I can remember is that a character, probably an enemy, turns out to be a computer. One that works with punch cards. It's situated in the attic of a house. IIRC, you work together with a female character. Heck, it might have been a movie, although I doubt it.
